  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The II. r. Wells ranch of 1900\nacres near Prosser, has come into\nthe possession of Hugo Spannagel,\nF. H. Mason, of the Holley, Mason,\nMarks company, and their en-\nployes. The consideration is $685.\n900, of which $4,000 was paid\ndown. Six hundred acres of the\nland will come under the United\nStates irrigation project at Sunny\nside. The syndicate intends to sell\nout the land in small ranches."
    }
